Class MapsForgeTileProvider

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.osmdroid.tileprovider.MapTileProviderBase
      • org.osmdroid.tileprovider.MapTileProviderArray
        • org.osmdroid.mapsforge.MapsForgeTileProvider
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    org.osmdroid.tileprovider.IMapTileProviderCallback

    public class MapsForgeTileProvider
extends org.osmdroid.tileprovider.MapTileProviderArray
    This lets you hook up multiple MapsForge files, it will render to the screen the first image that's available. Adapted from code from here: https://github.com/MKergall/osmbonuspack, which is LGPL http://www.salidasoftware.com/how-to-render-mapsforge-tiles-in-osmdroid/
